snippet.title: Witch Thief: Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Play as the snarky Witch Thief, on her quest to steal all the magic she possibly can! Naturally those who have the magic don't want to give it up so she does what she does best. That is, kicking in the front door and taking it all anyway!

Visit the Witch Thief Website
http://witchthief.games

Get Witch Thief on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/675480/Witch_Thief/
